title.en: Ane no Migawari de Konyaku shitara Naze ka Henkyou no Seijo to Yobareru you ni narimashita
Shakoukai na no Dokufu to Yobareru Watashi - Suteki na Henkyou Haku Reisoku ni Ude wo Orareta no de, Sekinin Totte Moraimasu
Meshimazu Onna Atsukaisareta no de Konyaku Haki Shitara, Naze ka Tsundere Ouji no Kokoro to Ibukuro Tsukanjaimashita
Akuyaku Reijou wa Boukensha ni Naru Tame Konyaku Haki wo Nozomimasu
Kyou kara Akujo ni narimasu! Tsukaisute no Migawari Seijo Nante Gomen desu
Konyaku Hakisareta Reijou wa Yajuu Henkyou Haku e Totsugu!
Shikkaku Seijo no Gekokujou - Sasensaki no Akuma na Shinpu-sama ni Naze ka Dekiaisareteimasu
Zense Seijo datta Watashi wa Kusushi ni narimashita
Kao Dake Seijo na no ni, Shi ni Modottara Reikoku Datta Koushaku-sama no Hon'ne ga Ama Sugimasu!
Danna-sama ga Chicchai Mofumofu ni narimashita ~Watashi wo Akujo da to Gokai shiteita no ni, Subete Gibo no Uso da to Kizuita you desu~
Konyaku Haki Sareta Kaedama Reijou, Hatsukoi no Toshiue Ouji ni Dekiai Sareru
Seiso Seijitsu ni Ikite Itara Konyakusha ni Uragirareta no de, Yarinaoshi no Sekai de wa Akuyaku Reijou to Shite Ikimasu
Uchi no Outaishi Denka wa Kyou mo Gu Kawaii ~Konyaku Haki desu no? Mochiron Kyakkashimasu keredo, Riyuu wa Kiite Sashiagemasu wa~
Kouri no Koushaku-sama to Karisome no Hanayome - Kozukuri Shitara Rikon no Hazu ga, Naze ka Chouaisaretemasu
Himegimi wa Wakaki Shougun ni Oboreru
Konyaku Haki Shiro to Iwareta no de Akuyaku Reijou wo Enjite Mitai to Omoimasu
Moto Noudai Joshi ni wa Akuyaku Reijou wa Muri desu!
